After Create you can browse what you create, change it and revert it.
After Change you should commit about the change.
After Revert you can make braches and commit about it.
After Update you could make a new branch or commit about the update in the same branch.
After Branch you should commit about the branch.
After Commit you can Publish.
---
Create : Make new repositry.
Browse : See the repositry.
Change : Edit on the files in the repositry.
Revert : Rewrite a commit of their are any mistake.
Update : Pull new file.
Branch : New file thats diffrent than the master.
Commit : Leave commit about what you did.
Publish : Push the project in new release.
